39:46.710 --> 39:48.620
[ Laughter ]

39:48.620 --> 39:54.500
♪ I'm still standing
after all this time ♪

39:54.500 --> 39:57.330
♪ Picking up
the pieces of my life ♪

39:57.330 --> 40:02.920
♪ Without you on my mind ♪

40:02.920 --> 40:09.250
♪ I'm still standing ♪

